content:
Yes, The Miracles had several other hit songs throughout their career. Here are a few examples:
 
1. "Shop Around" (1960)
2. "You've Really Got A Hold On Me" (1962)
3. "Mickey's Monkey" (1963)
4. "Going to a Go-Go" (1965)
5. "Tears of a Clown" (1970)

These songs are just a few examples of The Miracles' legacy of creating great music that has stood the test of time.
